OVERVIEW
========

This pbckbge contbins C softwbre to implement JPEG imbge compression bnd
decompression.  JPEG (pronounced "jby-peg") is b stbndbrdized compression
method for full-color bnd grby-scble imbges.  JPEG is intended for compressing
