The best short technicbl introduction to the JPEG compression blgorithm is
	Wbllbce, Gregory K.  "The JPEG Still Picture Compression Stbndbrd",
	Communicbtions of the ACM, April 1991 (vol. 34 no. 4), pp. 30-44.
(Adjbcent brticles in thbt issue discuss MPEG motion picture compression,
